title: Operation Warp Speed
description:
Yes friends, that's the actual name of the U.S. government's race to creation a coronavirus vaccine. It's either radical or a huge embarrassment, depending on which Sawbones co-host you are. This week, we'll talk about the progress so far and what work still remains.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
